    "en": {
      "name": "Artmegia Masterwork - Succession",
      "effect": "During the Main Phase: Fusion Summon 1 Fusion Monster from your Extra Deck, using monsters from your hand or field, including an \"Artmegia\" monster, then, if a card is in the Field Zone, the Summoned monster gains 500 ATK. During your Main Phase: You can banish this card from your GY, then target 3 \"Artmegia\" cards in your GY with different names; shuffle them into the Deck. You can only use each effect of \"Artmegia Masterwork - Succession\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
